Label: catalogNumber
Definition: An identifier (preferably unique) for the record within the data set or collection.

Label: scientificName
Definition: 'The full scientific name, with authorship and date information if known. When forming part of a dwc:Identification, this should be the name in lowest level taxonomic rank that can be determined. In the ''Primary hosts'' table it refers to the parasite.'

Label: associatedTaxa
Definition: 'A list (concatenated and separated) of identifiers or names of dwc:Taxon records and the associations of this dwc:Occurrence to each of them. All the associations listed here referes to the type ''host''.

Label: kingdom
Definition: 'The full scientific name of the kingdom in which the dwc:Taxon is classified. In the ''Primary hosts'' table it refers to the associatedTaxa.'

Label: phylum
Definition: 'The full scientific name of the phylum or division in which the dwc:Taxon is classified. In the ''Primary hosts'' table it refers to the associatedTaxa.'

Label: class
Definition: 'The full scientific name of the class in which the dwc:Taxon is classified. In the ''Primary hosts'' table it refers to the associatedTaxa.'

Label: order
Definition: 'The full scientific name of the order in which the dwc:Taxon is classified. In the ''Primary hosts'' table it refers to the associatedTaxa.'

Label: family
Definition: 'The full scientific name of the family in which the dwc:Taxon is classified. In the ''Primary hosts'' table it refers to the associatedTaxa.'

Label: genus
Definition: 'The full scientific name of the genus in which the dwc:Taxon is classified. In the ''Primary hosts'' table it refers to the associatedTaxa.'

Label: specificEpithet
Definition: 'The name of the first or species epithet of the dwc:scientificName. In the ''Primary hosts'' table it refers to the associatedTaxa.'
